                                <p>
                                  <hr>
                                  All items below are subject to Dues Paid Membership
                                  <hr>
                                </p>
                                <p>2. Online membership roster where you can view Club Member's pictures, email addresses, phone numbers, mailing addresses and 
                                callsigns if they choose to share.</p>
                                <p>3. The Net Control station schedule.</p>
                                <p>4. Our member's only forum.</p>
                                <br>
                                <p><em>If you are a SMARC member, please allow up to 48 hours for us to verify your membership. During this time, you will be able to access
                                 the Radio Market only.</em></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <script>        
                element.addEventListener('input',function(){this.value=this.value.toLowerCase()});​
            </script>
            <script>
                function ConfirmSubmit()
                {
                  var x = confirm("Please allow up to 48 hours for your membership verification to be approved. You will only have access to the Radio Market until you are verified. If you are not a SMARC member, you will only be allowed access to the radio market.");
                  if (x)
                      return true;
                  else
                    return false;
                }
            </script>
            <script>
              function onSubmit(token) {
                document.getElementById("regForm").submit();
              }
            </script>
            <script src="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js"></script>
          </div>
        </div>
